<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QLg88m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QLg88m.png&h=101a8560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0a1AOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0a1AOn.png&h=873d2d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GdFRmJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GdFRmJ.png&h=1f5cc154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9j080e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9j080e4.png&h=e00f3c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jz3VF1u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjz3VF1u.png&h=4b803cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tp9t01w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTp9t01w.png&h=9c276700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mF5Eoe7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmF5Eoe7.png&h=9ce93809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89cZ7GO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89cZ7GO.png&h=35fc1d15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20a28099a212f6b6ee4d05ba1771c5a41e63f9c3","tid":1237974,"uid":262425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"堅持到六月底<br />\n美國總統當勞侵將會在六月底G20峰會跟習近平談香港示威。香港示威已經納入G20侵習會議程。<br />\n美國支持香港反送中示威不是打咀炮，而是實實在在於美國國會立法監察香港人權和自治，懲治和制裁鎮壓示威的中港官員，共和及民主黨議員相繼向中港政府發出警告，押上他們的政治本錢，美國總統亦為香港學生出頭。示威和佔領行動一定要堅持到六月底G20峰會開幕，無論發生甚麼事，一定不要結束。<br />\n林鄭的假道歉全無誠意，政府說沒有將612示威定性為暴動，但是仍然會以暴動罪檢控學生，林鄭不下台，送中惡法只是暫緩。她說暫緩等同撤回，但是並非撤回。這樣的一切，只是想將示威平息下來，讓習近平可以在G20峰會向當勞侵說示威已經和平結束。<br />\n要是示威真的和平結束，美國要支持香港示威亦無能為力。相信中港政府會假讓步真打壓，不要墮入老共的緩兵之計。即使林鄭下台，送中惡法撤回，釋放部份學生，不再鎮壓示威，示威和佔領行動仍然要繼續下去。若果真的在峰會前結束示威，中共和港共會在G20峰會後來個共產黨式清算。<br />\n請各位相信我，示威行動一定要堅持到六月底。"},{"pid":"65cf1dbb1ef361476c1f4bbe77963bc02bff3f26","tid":1237974,"uid":182774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b249b0c0302e01d96ae7b1b93cfb37052f2c3bc","tid":1237974,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a2ff87bad6471275f899cede1c6abe957ee75e","tid":1237974,"uid":182774,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"無錯 再唔救義士 打一支強心針 我哋未必可以迎來下次嘅成功"},{"pid":"8a5a428f9adbceb393e64c2339cd72a9dda23254","tid":1237974,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔好諗呢D 野啦<br />\n你覺得會咩， 釋放姐係證明黑警唔岩<br />\n<br />\n咁冇咩理由唔告佢濫權"},{"pid":"f1c41be04e7dc27281cec47640d3a11d7b3b21f3","tid":1237974,"uid":207078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"65cf1dbb1ef361476c1f4bbe77963bc02bff3f26","tid":1237974,"uid":182774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91a2ff87bad6471275f899cede1c6abe957ee75e","tid":1237974,"uid":182774,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"無錯 兩樣都要！<br />\n但我怕好似魚革個時咁啫"},{"pid":"4b6d55f53f56374d451e7ddaa1dc6eea818904b1","tid":1237974,"uid":84075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"理性講 我覺得係最好機會收窄警權<br />\n以後未必有咁好既條件同情況<br />\n同埋少d比人打 同埋少d機會比人亂入罪<br />\n<br />\n我用緊電話打唔到好完整既陳述<br />\n希望仔細諗下"},{"pid":"f37bfd4d6e852609c47190c65a9c9b2343d0215a","tid":1237974,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a5a428f9adbceb393e64c2339cd72a9dda23254","tid":1237974,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔好諗呢D 野啦<br />\n你覺得會咩， 釋放姐係證明黑警唔岩<br />\n<br />\n咁冇咩理由唔告佢濫權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"唔知 近排睇返以前啲嘢 開始有啲感觸"},{"